@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.abs((v2 - wp.exp(tmp + 0.93)))
    v0 = (((v2 + 0.42 / tmp + 0.66) * wp.cos(tmp + 0.37)) * 0.66)
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.abs((tmp + 0.13 - v0 + 0.02)))
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.sin(wp.exp(tmp + 0.64)))
    data[tid] = v0
